The BesEvtGen is developed based on the EvtGen V00-11-07 by adding 
some models describing the charmonium decays as well as the baryon decays.
The BesEvtGen is the internal package of BOSS, which firs version is equivalent to 
external package of EvtGen-alpha-00-11-09. Ping Rong Gang, Sept. 14, 2007
